summary: This document is a declaration from the custodian of records for a high school in response to a court subpoena related to the case of United States v. Ghislaine Maxwell. It confirms that the records produced are true and correct copies responsive to the subpoena issued on July 30, 2021.
keyFacts: The document is a declaration of the custodian of records for a high school.
It responds to a court subpoena issued on July 30, 2021.
The case referenced is United States v. Ghislaine Maxwell, 20 Cr. 330 (AJN).
The declaration was executed on August 13, 2021.
The records produced are stated to be true and correct copies responsive to the subpoena.
